title: Mathematics Textbooks From Pre-Algebra to Linear Algebra
description:
Here is a complete series of textbooks beginning with Pre-Algebra and ending with Linear Algebra. Some of these are taken from torrents already present on Pirate Bay and others are from the net, I just wanted to create a central repository for some high quality Math Textbooks. Thanks to the Original uploaders!

Textbooks Included:

1.  College Algebra_Dawkins_2007
2.  Algebra 1_McGraw-Hill
3.  Elementary Algebra with Applications 3e_Wesner_2006
4.  Elementary Algebra_Burzynski_1989
5.  Algebra 2_McGraw-Hill_2008
6.  Intermediate Algebra_College of Redwoods_2007
7.  Calculus 1_Dawkins_2007
8.  Calculus 2_Dawkins_2007
9.  Calculus 3_Dawkins_2007
10. Differential Equations_Dawkins_2007
11. Linear Algebra_Dawkins_2007
12. Geometry_McGraw-Hill_2004
13. Pre-Algebra_McGraw-Hill
14. Pre-calculus_McGraw-Hill
15. Trigonometry with Applications 3e_Wesner_2007
16. College Algebra and Trigonometry with Applications 2e_Wesner_2007
17. Algebra & Trigonometry Review_Dawkins_2006
18. Algebra and Trigonometry 3e_Beecher_2007
